      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear how heavy and final that feeling of emptiness is, and I want to validate that this isn't just a temporary \"stage\" but a genuine sense of loss. When the part of you that felt alive or meaningful seems gone, the remaining routine can feel like a hollow performance, which is incredibly draining. Please know that your feelings are real, even if the situation feels permanent right now, and there is no need to pretend if you don't feel like you have to.",
